text:
LET'S START WITH SOME
INTERNATIONAL NEWS TONIGHT.

DO YOU GUYS KNOW THAT SONG
"DESPACITO?"

( CHEERS AND APPLAUSE )
YOU KNOW --

( SINGING )
WELL, THE GOVERNMENT OF MALAYSIA

HAS BANNED THE SONG FROM RADIO
AND TV IN THAT COUNTRY FOR
HAVING OBSCENE LYRICS.
THEY COULD BE RIGHT.

I'VE HEARD THIS SONG
TWO-THOUSAND TIMES AND I STILL
HAVE NO IDEA WHAT IT'S ABOUT.

( LAUGHTER )
SEE, THIS IS A BIG DIFFERENCE
BETWEEN THE U.S. AND MALAYSIA.

IN MALAYSIA, THE GOVERNMENT BANS
OBSCENE CONTENT.
HERE, THE PRESIDENT TWEETS IT.

( LAUGHTER )
( APPLAUSE )

ON THE BRIGHT SIDE, IT'S NOW
POSSIBLE TO GO AN ENTIRE DAY
WITHOUT HEARING DESPACITO.

YOU JUST HAVE TO MOVE TO
MALAYSIA.

AND THERE WAS SOME ALARMING
SCIENCE NEWS THIS WEEK.

NEW RESEARCH SHOWS THAT OVER THE
PAST 40 YEARS, THE SPERM COUNT

OF MEN HAS DECLINED BY OVER 50%
AND, IF IT KEEPS UP IT COULD

LEAD TO THE EXTINCTION OF THE
HUMAN RACE.

( APPLAUSE )
I KNOW WHY YOU'RE CLAPPING.

REGGIE'S LIKE, SHORTER LINES AT
DISNEYLAND!

( LAUGHTER )
AND THIS WAS INTERESTING.

APPARENTLY, THE STUDY WHERE THEY
EXAMINED THE SPERM OF THOUSANDS

OF MEN, WAS CONDUCTED BY--
YO MAMA.

( LAUGHTER )
YO MOMMA.

( LAUGHTER )
AND THIS WAS A CRAZY STORY.

A TEXAS-BASED COFFEE COMPANY
HAS HAD TO RECALL A TYPE OF

COFFEE THEY MAKE BECAUSE IT
CONTAINS AN INGREDIENT SIMILAR
TO VIAGRA.

NOW, THIS PRODUCT HAD ALREADY
GONE ON SALE.

AND THE CUSTOMERS WHO TRIED IT
FOUND OUT ABOUT IT THE HARD WAY.

( LAUGHTER )
( PIANO RIFF )
THAT WAS THE BAD NEWS.

THE GOOD NEWS, AT LEAST YOU'VE
GOT A PLACE TO HOLD YOUR DONUT.

( LAUGHTER )
YOU WERE LIKE -- IT'S FINE.

( LAUGHTER )
FINALLY, THIS WAS OUTRAGEOUS.

A FIVE-YEAR-OLD GIRL WHO RAN A
LEMONADE STAND IN LONDON WAS

FINED $195 FOR NOT HAVING THE
PROPER TRADING PERMIT.

SEE, THIS IS WHY I MAKE MY KIDS
OPEN ALL THEIR LEMONADE STANDS
OFFSHORE ON THE CAYMAN ISLANDS.

( LAUGHTER )
IF YOU ASK ME, THESE COPS MADE A
MISTAKE.
